channel.title: Newbie Error
channel.description:
Hey people, my first post, please dont spam, flame or call me ugly names. Its mean :(. This is my first time trying to run a server and i keep getting an error. - d d s p 3 c - .. Online! Connection accepted from ip72-216-46-187.pn.at.cox.net: 1469. Client type: high memory version UserId: 96879658 Papa is signing onto server. Papa: character file not found. Papa: moreinfo file not found. LOADED: 3 java.net.SocketException: Unrecognized Windows Sockets error: -1: socket availab le at java.net.PlainSocketImpl.socketAvailable(Native Method) at java.net.PlainSocketImpl.available(Unknown Source) at java.net.SocketInputStream.available(Unknown Source) at client.packetProcess(client.java:18870) at client.packetSending(client.java:18856) at PlayerHandler.process(PlayerHandler.java:138) at server.main(server.java:53) pimpscape Server [fatal] - exception Game saved for player Papa ClientHandler: Client Papa disconnected. Connection accepted from ip72-216-46-178.pn.at.cox.net: 1471. Client type: high memory version UserId: 96879658 Papa is signing onto server. LOADED: 3 java.net.SocketException: Unrecognized Windows Sockets error: -1: socket availab le at java.net.PlainSocketImpl.socketAvailable(Native Method) at java.net.PlainSocketImpl.available(Unknown Source) at java.net.SocketInputStream.available(Unknown Source) at client.packetProcess(client.java:18870) at client.packetSending(client.java:18856) at PlayerHandler.process(PlayerHandler.java:138) at server.main(server.java:53) pimpscape Server [fatal] - exception Game saved for player Papa ClientHandler: Client Papa disconnected.
Can anyone help? It's probally gunna be something stupid i didnt notice or see.. Thanks a ton and try to help me pl0x :D. Byez
